<%- @page_title = "eXtension Sign up - Missing Information" -%>

<div class="well">

<h2>Missing Reset Token</h2>

<p>We're so sorry, the link that you clicked to confirm your email address had a missing or invalid confirmation token that we use internally to verify that you received our email to you.</p>

<p>We aren't completely sure why this happened. We would very much like to help you get your email confirmed and also to find out more information about your email client so that we can improve our confirmation process. Let us know in our support form below.</p>

<p>You can also trying <%= link_to("sending another confirmation email", accounts_reset_password_path) %> with a new link to your email account</p>

<p>If you do send us a support question, please include in your description:
  <ul>
    <li>The email client that you are using to read your email</li>
    <li>Uploading a screen capture of how the email looks in your email client would help us tremendously!</li>
  </ul>
</p>

<p>Email us a bug report at <a href="mailto:contact-us@extension.org">contact-us@extension.org</a></p>
</div>
